lt;p&gt;We&amp;rsquo;ve innovated our way out of previous traps&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Brett:&lt;/strong&gt;&#xA;If you&amp;rsquo;re an academic, being able to explain all of the problems that are out there and how dangerous these problems are and why you need funding to look at them in more depth appears to be the intellectually serious position; whereas, someone who claims that we can solve it sounds a little bit kumbaya.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
